_directives.name: skip
_directives.description: Directs the executor to skip this field or fragment when the `if` argument is true.

_directives.name: include
_directives.description: Directs the executor to include this field or fragment only when the `if` argument is true.

_directives.name: cost
_directives.description: The cost directives is used to express the complexity of a field.

args.name: complexity
args.description: Defines the complexity of the field.

args.name: multipliers
args.description: Defines field arguments that act as complexity multipliers.

args.name: policy
args.description: The name of the authorization policy that determines access to the annotated resource.

args.name: roles
args.description: Roles that are allowed to access to the annotated resource.

_directives.name: deprecated

args.name: reason
